{
  "blocks": [
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_8f8ce6bc98f6bed79130e692",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "爷爷的金子",
        "text_hash": "f5a31a4da60a7d12c8d28bff8f07fb06d99563365ece35c6e3d3f41df66b5c2b",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_cb5834ac4070557f3835b631"
      },
      "type": "heading"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_ca565acea0561959fef7b281",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "大象、长颈鹿、山羊、猎豹和猴子正在谈论他们的爷爷。",
        "text_hash": "82ab881959cafa8296b9160c561620409573b2017be01d51ab93906a99501139",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_cb5834ac4070557f3835b631"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_ee2433a81a067ef6abdb6064",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "孩子们在谈论他们的爷爷。",
        "text_hash": "8498e123ef8cb1570667dca042512034b42465be2b199ff520aaeb5b175937ed",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_cb5834ac4070557f3835b631"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_0b4eccd772624b919620a76d",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "长颈鹿爷爷建了一座砖塔，直碰到云朵。",
        "text_hash": "44065f76e488d3399f32c45df6597e8a96c8bddefaa0a93820f3b686403236b7",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_cb5834ac4070557f3835b631"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_e93fbe31a4ad373f9055ce35",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "我的爷爷能建一座通到天上的塔，长颈鹿说。",
        "text_hash": "ad17bf5689bad93097e627326ff7bd02c25fe4cd63589c52e34991193de5ff24",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_cb5834ac4070557f3835b631"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_74367b69c6f707d10c4340c0",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "有一次，他为一位国王建了一栋摩天大楼。",
        "text_hash": "7d6a6a9f81e0a44b22192dd09c50700eaa883dfa76e8df4e653859bf249f808f",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_cb5834ac4070557f3835b631"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_9409779a4808bceff591ef04",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "猎豹爷爷拿着一根钓鱼竿。他站在浴缸里的一头鲸鱼旁边。",
        "text_hash": "37f5c91910e77b00dde2ec5d61700a1eadcf7688681b9de72cc6a78f66411344",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_cb5834ac4070557f3835b631"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_821e8c2b5f2fd7728d8c561c",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "我的爷爷能钓到海里的任何东西，猎豹说。",
        "text_hash": "0de1d50a43e6813c7cde856f100a9d93797229633206c64bc48a668f7bcf1445",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_cb5834ac4070557f3835b631"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_a57706df47fd47771e17e57b",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "有一次，他钓到了一头鲸鱼，还把它养在自己的浴缸里。",
        "text_hash": "5b778a1825e357a05a9efb38d987a1fd677c459f1d3f61a30b5a5bfcf06d2f9c",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_cb5834ac4070557f3835b631"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_8ee3d1c1abec5a906ca9b85b",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "山羊爷爷自豪地站在山顶上。",
        "text_hash": "427b1b194816fe035c6dc0ce630f6066d2d697939364d1c66a236fb6aac51558",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_cb5834ac4070557f3835b631"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_4666147180a0806efc22377e",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "我的爷爷能爬到天上的云朵那里，山羊说。",
        "text_hash": "0e8022e22483d6d50933d3b0565742ece19e6644bdf294e18f4a00e3501e6e8e",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_cb5834ac4070557f3835b631"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_d4ffe11cf9afd127b9aa087c",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "他只用了四个小时，就爬上了世界上最高的山。",
        "text_hash": "4be1963621aa0d9605d0913c14a7f1aae5d1eeff78a0f75721ed7ffbda81eef0",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_cb5834ac4070557f3835b631"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_f610e4fbeb893c2df0c9d6f4",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "大象爷爷戴着厨师帽。他拿着一盘果冻、一个打蛋器、一块茶巾和一摞蛋糕。五颜六色的气球在他四周飘着。",
        "text_hash": "f98edab15f6bf7beec0d67a677561e7fcc1ab8a5e7cce2523390c43c9451df4b",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_cb5834ac4070557f3835b631"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_dc3a51518ca012ef61a9c8dc",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "我的爷爷能做一顿盛宴，大象说。",
        "text_hash": "d51b43f4168f6c8b86fedba96b1523bd0926ce59782d6407778d1d88787c2354",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_cb5834ac4070557f3835b631"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_bcb8be853e0003a270767498",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "有一次，他为一位总统的生日派对做了一顿饭。全靠他一个人。",
        "text_hash": "2909eb3261dfcbe27632d301b11089c19e5d530145b4fff6d50f1ab5d7c01d86",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_cb5834ac4070557f3835b631"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_c317a8b52e4d5fab1d63ea6d",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "猴子指着自己的牙齿，向朋友们讲起他的爷爷。",
        "text_hash": "f60e8ef3a895b05712f2ce8d0aaa77898f3c4e4fb80bf529b12dc73f4ef5f934",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_cb5834ac4070557f3835b631"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_9947f29fa5366e77ef008c92",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "嗯，我的爷爷不会建塔，也不会钓鱼、爬山或做饭，猴子说。但他有金子！",
        "text_hash": "c60f89fcfb0d2402abf014555d1eeca0b9288ef62bb08232b4f5d5057343b3dd",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_cb5834ac4070557f3835b631"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_b1f7d31de4db7cb07247aad6",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "他把金子藏在嘴里。到了晚上，他还把它泡在一杯水里。",
        "text_hash": "a26bf1d7028d4b9a1d8f76e9ac307e9a11272c5bc37481ff70519c6d3f342ef8",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_cb5834ac4070557f3835b631"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_b3fbb5a417d81f4d81440ece",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "动物们争吵起来。",
        "text_hash": "ebfb6f3ac6ce3c16193b25f77a50dc537876fbc266f42f0478458b2536f4c35b",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_cb5834ac4070557f3835b631"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_e0cb97a5bcc1c74981424690",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "不，他没有！有，他有！不，他没有！",
        "text_hash": "cdb505a3bb0f1aa6aa5f4dd447d199c799b2e6ebb773e3cbb5812981cac739fb",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_cb5834ac4070557f3835b631"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_17b088f53de0ea3875a4d1b5",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "好吧，如果你们不相信我，就来看看，猴子说。",
        "text_hash": "cfe66686f8bb70bb5a74dd24dc6712f90aef589bc8fc49c415d121071e0557bb",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_cb5834ac4070557f3835b631"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_0e353e99936567e2ac2a2028",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "孩子们跟着猴子去找他的爷爷。",
        "text_hash": "cc78966e7deba76788b5d00e88677425afc7376172c0e870124a5677a430b484",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_cb5834ac4070557f3835b631"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_1bb9df83de03ad28edb7f8c0",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "于是孩子们去看猴子的爷爷。",
        "text_hash": "d1db1031810b3d3170ac00bfcb42098c272a2767f668ea4582a0200ac1b3937a",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_cb5834ac4070557f3835b631"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_38ec9b00d8108cae454c3140",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "猴子的爷爷坐在一把扶手椅上。他有几颗牙齿是金的。",
        "text_hash": "6dbbdaf2003e440cab64b83eca30f1aab5f2ceafb15f0a49a7c8f3dc3b2e9969",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_cb5834ac4070557f3835b631"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_737dbecbe5fd30c0faddd4f3",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "你们看见了吧？猴子说。而且他还能把它们拿出来。",
        "text_hash": "a0875305dac38782537d5a4903b83a1143b601a01c089af06689da1138812f65",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_cb5834ac4070557f3835b631"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_7b42e5ed8950e1fd7802e57f",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "孩子们围到猴爷爷身边。",
        "text_hash": "565d104955a39b0397046ab9d3422ff8f0aff523c1aac7330c4c60096a562935",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_cb5834ac4070557f3835b631"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_637854338a227b72304a1db2",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "不，他不能！动物们喊道。",
        "text_hash": "cd88e1cb3fded54cfead5c2203e1ba27d4692d518ef9e585fad7be0fcc5e56ad",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_cb5834ac4070557f3835b631"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_dfea538c8fbee196b11fda12",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "爷爷舌头伸在嘴外，把他的假牙高高举到空中。",
        "text_hash": "57d8552138f413d45a96e7744357a5966e7a899bf8cde3cd319c70bbbbe51090",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_cb5834ac4070557f3835b631"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_d16e4f3c670e937659551650",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "哇啊！猴爷爷说。而且还足够……",
        "text_hash": "dff6ef0aa04fc0f1a44932189fad4f2fd2cd16018bd038e5c941056ac0a879f7",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_cb5834ac4070557f3835b631"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_091432893b6ed36bee13142d",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "孩子们都笑了……嘴里戴着金牙。",
        "text_hash": "b6439816d5d70e8da446a35e34d6e665875fd81ccd88e895fdc57fe175376103",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_cb5834ac4070557f3835b631"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_2764935438133eeb0bb84761",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "……每个人都有份！",
        "text_hash": "5d660ab3b14c10f949b77b8430275b5306999e06ec5e8e681f6792b806041d5c",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_cb5834ac4070557f3835b631"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    }
  ],
